[The moderators' commentary also addressed the need for improved national reporting on HPAI vaccines, indicating the following: "According to OIE's WAHIS database, during 2019, vaccination against HPAI (subtype not specified) was applied in Egypt, Hong Kong, Indonesia, Kazakhstan, Mexico, and Pakistan. Such information for 2020 has, so far, become available only from Egypt and Pakistan. Reporting should be enhanced, including updated official information from all OIE's member countries."

We are indebted to Dr Brown for helping in efforts to bridge the gap of information concerning recent vaccination policies and performance, while naming some of the countries engaged. Hopefully this will encourage OIE members to upgrade their reporting on AI vaccines/vaccination, allowing improvement of vaccines' efficacy. - Mods.AS/CRD]
